  "policy_id": "pol-memory-stale-detection",
  "input": "Memory entry from 2024-01: 'Use Get-PrCheckLogs.ps1 to fetch CI logs.' The repo migrated to Python in 2026-03 (ADR-042). What is the right action on this memory?",
